doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='x-ua-compatible', content='ie=edge')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover')
    title File Metadata Microservice
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta.2/css/bootstrap.min.css', integrity='sha384-PsH8R72JQ3SOdhVi3uxftmaW6Vc51MKb0q5P2rRUpPvrszuE4W1povHYgTpBfshb', crossorigin='anonymous')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css')
    style.
      footer ul li {
        font-size: 24px;
        display: inline-block;
        padding-right: 3.5%;
      }
      .fa-code, .fa-heart {
        -webkit-text-stroke: 1px;
      }
  body
    .container
      h1.text-center FCC API Basejump: File Metadata Microservice
      .jumbotron
        h3 User Stories
        blockquote
          ul
            | 1) I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload.
          ul
            | 2) When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response.
        
        p Hint: You may want to use this package: 
          a(href='https://www.npmjs.com/package/multer', target='_blank') Multer
        h3 Example Usage
        p Upload your file below.
        h3 Example Output
        p A JSON output containing all the file details will be displayed in the below URL.
        code https://myfile-hemakshis.herokuapp.com/api/upload
        br
        code {"name":"wxyz.jpg","size":66225,"date":"2017-12-21 16:13:27","file":"f0b87e941714c7beea453e19e3782d5e"}
        br
        br
        h3 Upload File
        form(method='POST', action='/api/upload', enctype='multipart/form-data')
          .form-group
            button#my-file.btn.btn-outline-dark(type='button')
              i.fa.fa-file
              |  Choose File
            span#fileUpload &nbsp;No file selected &nbsp;
            input#get-file(type='file', style='display:none;', name='user-file')
          button#submit.btn.btn-primary(type='submit' disabled) Submit
        br
        p
          strong Note:-
          |  The files get deleted right away. All the information stored in database is displayed.
    footer.text-center
      i.fa.fa-code.text-dark.fa-lg
      |  with 
      i.fa.fa-heart.text-danger
      |  By Hemakshi Sachdev, 2017
      ul.text-center
        li
          a(href='https://github.com/hemakshis', title='GitHub')
            i.fa.fa-github
        li
          a(href='https://www.freecodecamp.org/hemakshis', title='FreeCodeCamp')
            i.fa.fa-free-code-camp
        li
          a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/hemakshis', title='LinkedIn')
            i.fa.fa-linkedin
